comments: Williams (NOP) establishes himself in a screening position in Westbrook's (HOU) path and does not deliver the contact.
Ingram (NOP) establishes screening position and firms up in House Jr.'s (HOU) path.
Harden (HOU) and Redick (NOP) engage and disengage off ball without affecting the other's FOM.
Tucker (HOU) legally contests Ingram's (NOP) jump shot attempt.
Williams (NOP) makes contact with Westbrook's (HOU) head during rebounding, but it is marginal and does not affect his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Ingram (NOP) briefly places his left hand on Harden's (HOU) hip but does not affect his FOM.
Ball (NOP) legally contest Harden's (HOU) jump shot.
Tucker (HOU) and Williams (NOP) engage and disengage during the rebound.
Ball (NOP) maintains legal  guarding position during Westbrook's (HOU) driving shot attempt.
Tucker (HOU) cleanly dislodges the ball during rebounding with Hart (NOP).
Harden (HOU) briefly grasps Redick's (NOP) arm as he moves through the lane but the contact is marginal.
Williams (NOP) establishes himself in a screening position in Harden's (HOU) path and does not deliver the contact.
Hart (NOP) makes marginal contact with Tucker (HOU) during rebounding and does not affect his ability to retrieve the ball.
Hart (NOP) moves into Harden (HOU) and makes leg-to-leg contact that affects his SQBR.
Harden (HOU) places two hands on Redick (NOP) as he moves around the perimeter during the inbound and the contact affects his FOM.
Hart (NOP) commits the take foul on Westbrook (HOU).
Redick (NOP) makes marginal contact with Gordon's (HOU) front that does not affect his ability to defend.
Gordon (HOU) makes marginal contact with Ball's (NOP) side after he picks up his dribble and does not affect his SQBR.
Westbrook (HOU) legally contests Hart's (NOP) jump shot attempt.
